    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "Four new Bent-toed geckos (Cyrtodactylus Gray: Squamata: Gekkonidae) from northeast India" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897019>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897023>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897041>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897017>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897013> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897019>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A: Dorsal view, B: ventral view, C: details of dorsal pholidosis, D: dorsal view of head, E: ventral view of head and F: lateral view of head of the holotype of Cyrtodactylus karsticola sp. nov. (MZMU2155)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4897019/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897023>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Live specimens of Cyrtodactylus karsticola sp. nov. (A and B are the dorsal and ventral view of the holotype; C and D are uncollected specimens)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4897023/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897041>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. The arrangement of A: precloacofemoral pores in Cyrtodactylus karsticola sp. nov.; B: precloacal pores in Cyrtodactylus agarwali sp. nov.; C: precloacal pores in Cyrtodactylus aaronbaueri sp. nov.and D: precloacal pores in Cyrtodactylus bengkhuaiai sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4897041/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897017>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Maximum Likelihood phylogeny of Indo-Burmese Cyrtodactylus; numbers at nodes represent bootstrap support (Preceding the species name is NCBI accession number and in the parenthesis is the museum catalogue number of the specimen)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4897017/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4897013>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Elevation map showing the type localities of new species and Cyrtodactylus species included in the comparisons: 1. Cyrtodactylus karsticola sp. nov. (black star); 2. C. agarwali sp. nov. (black circle); 3. C. aaronbaueri sp. nov. (black triangle); 4. C. bengkhuaiai sp. nov. (black tilted square); 5. C. montanus; 6. C. tripuraensis; 7. C. khasiensis; 8. C. jaintiaensis; 9. C. guwahatiensis; 10. C. urbanus; 11. C. septentrionalis; 12. C. kazirangaensis; 13. C. nagalandensis; 14. C. arunachalensis; 15. C. markuscombaii and C. martinstolli; 16. C. himalayicus; 17. C. cayuensis; 18. C. tamaiensis; 19. C. ayeyarwadyensis; 20. C. mandalayensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4897013/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

